{"tid":551071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"養龜嘅入一入嚟 唔該！（有圖）","createTime":"2018-02-05T10:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T13:34:49.000Z","uid":73694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37ae65db484cce5c293859d9e1e43fa0ab4cca3a","tid":551071,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"最近天氣凍左好多<br />\n我見啲水溫（溫度計 ）15-18度<br />\n上個星期就幫佢買左條暖管 <br />\n開太陽燈個陣就較凍少少水溫<br />\n開uvb個陣就較返暖少少<br />\n但唔知點解佢成日都匿埋<br />\n但夜晚又好似出多啲黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/181905_aca91d3956f0d95216f524077d1ff3f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F181905_aca91d3956f0d95216f524077d1ff3f2.png&h=2f2ab1c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/181913_0148e243bc6a2a06cd16ccaa53ec4eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F181913_0148e243bc6a2a06cd16ccaa53ec4eee.png&h=2db10904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢會唔會有病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申養左4個月<br />\n有食野 仲幾多下"},{"pid":"75ee8557a952148bb6f64aa64ad6176ba7eec34f","tid":551071,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9921831a7edce77948d08b0e8c9f7c5faf9bc039","tid":551071,"uid":73694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face